<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>DTG Addition</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
  <div class="text-center mb-4 p-3">
    <img src="/images/trinity-health-banner.png" alt="Trinity Health Banner" style="max-width: 350px;">
  </div>
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h1 class="h3 mb-0">DTG Addition</h1>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p>Add <%= entry.data['First Name'] %> <%= entry.data['Middle Initial'] || '' %> <%= entry.data['Last Name'] %> to the Pyxis ES Group</p>
            
            <h5>PowerShell Command:</h5>
            <div class="bg-light border p-3 mb-3">
              <code>Add-ADGroupMember -Identity "Pyxis ES Users" -Members "<%= (entry.data['First Name'] + '.' + entry.data['Last Name']).toLowerCase() %>"</code>
            </div>
            
            <p>Copy and paste the above command into PowerShell to add the user to the group.</p>
            
            <form action="/stage/<%= stage %>/<%= entry.id %>" method="POST">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Confirm DTG Addition</button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <footer class="text-center mt-5">
    <p>DTG Pyxis Access v1.0.0</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>